PA1: Extrema

Purpose: The purpose of this program is to use recursion to find the minimum
and maximum elements of an array.

Files:

README
Makefile
Extrema.java

Notes:

i. Wrote the base case to make sure the array has more than one element.
ii. Recurse from the middle until they reach the base case.
iii. Compare left and right arrays to find the minimum or maximum.  